// outputs~returns&#58; 15[/code:1ougmo9n]

whereas, the need for the 'CDATA' tags:

[code:1ougmo9n]&lt;function name=&quot;game_over_function&quot;&gt;&lt;!&#91;CDATA&#91;
  if (player&#46;current_life &lt;= 0) {
